dct_title_s: Estância climática de Campos do Jordão : associação dos proprietários de hotéis e similares de Campos do Jordão, escala 1:10.000
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by spot heights. Map shows municipal and district administrative boundaries, roads, high volage lines, railroads, and churches. Includes index, telephone directories, and coat of arms. With a color illustration of the coat of arms.
